  "text": "The sensitivity analysis of physiological markers identified two outliers: the study by Schmitz and Melinda, in which the duration of intervention lasted for 6 to 12 months, while the durations were 12 to 15 weeks in other studies. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] Therefore, it is likely that the duration of exercise intervention is the source of heterogeneity among these results.",
